  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Bakuton Clan, Level 12+</p><p>When something explodes, you just can't contain yourself. You find that all explosions push you ever closer to ecstasy. You gain the following Benefits;</p><p>• When you roll a Shrapnel die, you treat 1's as 2.</p><p>• You gain +2 additional shrapnel die.</p><p>• Whenever you roll the maximum damage on a Shrapnel Die or a Bakuton clan Hijutsu damage die add +3 Force damage to the total damage dealt.</p><p>• When you would cast Explosion Release: Tower of the Sun, you instead do leave behind a corpse. If you are revived after casting this jutsu, you are unable to cast that ever again.</p>",
